    "Apple Foundation Models are on-device models that will process all information locally on your Mac. Requires macOS 26 or later with Apple Intelligence enabled." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Apple Foundation Models are on-device models that will process all information locally on your Mac. Requires macOS 26 or later with Apple Intelligence enabled."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Los modelos base de Apple son modelos integrados en el dispositivo que procesarán toda la información localmente en su Mac. Requiere macOS 26 o posterior con Apple Intelligence habilitado."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Apple Foundation Modelsは、Mac上でローカルにすべての情報を処理するデバイス内モデルです。Apple Intelligenceが有効なmacOS 26以降が必要です。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Apple Foundation 模型是设备端模型，将在您的 Mac 上本地处理所有信息。需要 macOS 26 或更高版本，并启用 Apple Intelligence。"
